    <item>
      <title>欧盟寻求妥协以扩大对乌克兰的零关税贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/eu-finds-compromise-to-extend-tarrif-free-trade-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟成员国周三达成了一项艰难的妥协，将乌克兰的免关税贸易再延长一年，因为欧盟各地的农民一直在抗议从这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家进口粮食。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/eu-finds-compromise-to-extend-tarrif-free-trade-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:08:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Aethon 表示，投资者认为海恩斯维尔页岩公司 IPO 的时机已经成熟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/investors-see-haynesville-shale-as-ripe-for-ipos-aethon-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据少数人持股的 Aethon Energy Management 称，投资者对天然气丰富的路易斯安那州海恩斯维尔页岩的更多公开交易钻探公司的兴趣日益浓厚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/investors-see-haynesville-shale-as-ripe-for-ipos-aethon-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:08:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
