      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Hedgeye 将其命名为一个简短的创意并暴跌 50%，Reddit 暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/reddit-tumbles-as-hedgeye-names-it-a-short-idea-sees-50-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Hedgeye Risk Management 发布一份报告将 Reddit 视为做空想法并表示其交易价格应比当前水平低约 50% 后，Reddit Inc. 股价有望创下该社交媒体公司上市以来的最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/reddit-tumbles-as-hedgeye-names-it-a-short-idea-sees-50-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:14:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官裁定 SEC 针对 Coinbase 的诉讼可以继续进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/sec-suit-against-coinbase-can-go-forward-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约一名联邦法官裁定，美国证券交易委员会可以继续对美国最大的加密货币交易平台 Coinbase Inc. 提起诉讼，称该公司未能注册为证券公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/sec-suit-against-coinbase-can-go-forward-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可价格从反弹后的短暂下跌反弹至 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/cocoa-fluctuates-as-investors-take-profit-after-rally-to-10-000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约可可期货小幅走高，扭转了价格短暂下跌的局面，因投资者在价格上涨至每吨 10,000 美元上方后获利了结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/cocoa-fluctuates-as-investors-take-profit-after-rally-to-10-000</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:46:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待沃勒言论，新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/emerging-markets-fall-with-caution-on-us-inflation-yuan-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数新兴市场货币周三走软，因为交易员在本季度末之前重新平衡了投资组合，并且市场等待美联储官员的言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/emerging-markets-fall-with-caution-on-us-inflation-yuan-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
